ygData.messageBody:
Hi all, I am an enchanter on tallon zek server and just got my jewelry
skill able to do electrum. Wow 400pp, thats a bit. Anyways, I think I am
the first in my area to have electrum jewelry so I was wondering at what
prices I can sell my items, here is teh list of decent items
+4 chr bracelets
+2 wis earrings
+3 agi rings
+2 int necklace
+1 str earrings
and the jade +10 mana hp and 2ac

Also, can I start to make the cool stuff like the ruby veil or opal stuff
and at what prices do these usually go for? thanx guys
